dct_description_sm: With a legend of public buildings, places of worship, outdoor spaces, and monuments. Map shows street names, parks, cemeteries, schools, and planned sites of construction. Verso shows inset map of Tarbes and other cities and points of interest in the region Occitanie, southwestern France. Verso includes index of points of interest, tourist information, text, and advertisements. "Reproduction interdite."
